{"tid":1233353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［謹記］唔好再擋cctvb拍攝","createTime":"2019-06-16T18:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T18:54:09.000Z","uid":263105,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"775c0806c3ac6d6ced6bb6b9c23ef936c1617c57","tid":1233353,"uid":263105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:23:53.000Z","msg":"今日有出去行既都知cctvb成為過街老鼠<br />\n去到邊比人噓到邊<br />\n但請各位謹記我地只需要舉起轉台牌 <br />\n並<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔係防礙佢地既拍攝</span><br />\n因為如果係咁 我地一樣係防礙新聞自由<br />\n佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">有權拍</span> 我地<span style=\"color: red;\">有權表達意見</span><br />\n到最後佢地播啲咩都係上面話事<br />\n唔好難為前線！<br />\n記得守住唔好比地方人地抽秤！"},{"pid":"356e6618f074999b395c815a7094cf9fd806a9e3","tid":1233353,"uid":62097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:38:36.000Z","msg":"唔知啲機防唔防水呢"},{"pid":"6a81787580708b755c9ef6a4b8c4a1dc905cfb8e","tid":1233353,"uid":261998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:46:29.000Z","msg":"佢地訪問都收起咪牌<br />\n<br />\n另外我見有個巴打係直播個陣舉海報，好榜樣！"},{"pid":"caaca05f10b7fe52020ed8089876eb3e95f56341","tid":1233353,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:49:31.000Z","msg":"而家仲做大台既都無乜良心 或者係港豬<br />\n洗同佢客氣咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前線crew驚就最好添啦 最好個個劈炮唔撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a509103cd2af6d747724fabf27c67426cf0359","tid":1233353,"uid":242912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:53:43.000Z","msg":"成班圍撚住佢嗌 事事但但<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後條友走左去食堙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec743f2af6e11413718c9ee0f10ca6ee8810f742","tid":1233353,"uid":126317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:54:09.000Z","msg":"TVB 好事多為，忍左佢好多年了，<br />\n我諗全香港有二百萬人，都想佢繼續做過街老鼠，步亞視後塵⋯⋯<br />\n亦相信今日好多人返屋企之後，掉左個TVB box 落垃圾桶<br />\n<br />\n市民的眼睛是雪亮的，即使佢依家同林鄭割蓆都無用"}]}